10:01 AM 12/12/2016
					




One of our core specialties is minimizing the environmental impacts of metal production by turning waste products into useful materials and helping create a greener world.  Our SteelPhalt™ business leads the way in the use of steel slag for asphalt road construction. 

							



Click here for a short video. 










							In the natural gas industry, efficiency and speed are essential to market success. CenterPoint, Harsco Industrial Air-X-Changers’ new manufacturing hub, puts productivity at the center of our focus.
							


Learn how Harsco Industrial Air-X-Changers’ commitment to lean manufacturing is helping us meet customer demand.









