Harsco Industrial IKG is a registered trademark of Harsco Corporation.
A Division of Harsco Corporation



Harsco Industrial IKG has pioneered grating industry solutions for nearly 100 years and continues to be one of the world´s leading producers of a broad range of high quality steel bar grating and aluminum bar grating. Harsco Industrial IKG is distinguished by its unparalleled metal grating manufacturing capability and dedication to value-added customer service. Our primary grating product lines include fabricated grating, mezzanine grating, stock welded steel grating and aluminum grating panels, and Mebac® Safety Products. Harsco Industrial IKG was formerly IKG Industries.









