Home: Products

Harsco Industrial IKG Product Line

Harsco Industrial IKG (IKG) is one of the world’s leading manufacturers of high quality steel and aluminum bar grating. Our dedicated, knowledgeable grating products personnel offer tailor-made grating solutions to your challenging situations.
IKG has four primary product lines: Stock Panels, Fabricated Grating, Mezzanine Grating and Mebac®. Click on any one to learn more about the products and services we provide.







                Stock Panels

Harsco Industrial IKG (IKG) manufactures high quality, reliable and aesthetically pleasing stock grating panels. Produced in our own, highly automated plants, they are available on immediate or short-term notice. 
More Info

 








                Fabricated Grating

Harsco Industrial IKG’s (IKG) full line of Fabricated Gratings are manufactured at our plants and sized exactly for your complex floor patterns and hard-to-fit areas. We provide professional design, estimating, engineering and project management assistance, unsurpassed manufacturing capacity, and quick turnaround and delivery, giving our customers a better product in a timely fashion and at a competitive price. 
More Info

 








                Mezzanine Grating

Harsco Industrial IKG’s (IKG) Mezzanine Grating specialists deal only with materials handling applications and are focused on cost effective solutions for your projects. With superior Mezzanine manufacturing capacity, professional engineering design and layout and multiple shipping points, IKG is your premier Mezzanine source.
More Info

 








                Mebac® "The First Family of Slip Resistance"

Mebac® is available only from Harsco Industrial IKG (IKG) in five grades of slip-resistant coating. A valuable part of any slip and fall loss prevention program, Mebac® is durable and low maintenance, apply it to your grating once and it provides slip resistance for years. 
More Info

 








                Harsco Industrial IKG GrateCoat®

Through a multi-million dollar investment in powder coat technology, Harsco Industrial IKG (IKG) is the first grating manufacturer to offer powder coat finish as a standard paint for bar grating. Our new GrateCoat® finish is available in standard colors of Black and Gray,  or we can match the paint colors on your existing applications.
More Info

 








                Specialty Products

As the industry leader in Specialty Products in both steel and aluminum, Harsco Industrial IKG (IKG) offers a wide range of swaged, Safe-T-Grid®, pressure locked and heavy weld grating products, manufactured to NAAMM standards and customized to your needs. IKG has over 100 years’ experience in sales engineering, project management and quality control, which means fewer problems for you in the field.
More Info

 








                GrateGuard™

An Innovative new approach to high security fencing. Our skilled sales personnel and engineering staff are highly knowledgably in the perimeter industry, providing solutions to customers in a wide range of commercial applications. Discover how GrateGuard™ can fulfill your specific project needs.
More Info

More Info

 









 


