HomepageExplore our businessesHarsco Metals & MineralsHarsco RailAir-X-ChangersIKGPatterson-KelleyFinancial InformationFinancial Press ReleasesStock InformationDividend and Split HistoryWebcastsPresentationsEvents CalendarAnalyst CoverageContact Us Home > HomepageCreating Value for Our ShareholdersHarsco has three market leading businesses and the Company is driving to capture profitable growth opportunities, balance and optimize its portfolio, achieve Continuous Improvement and generate returns above its cost of capital. The Company’s focus in its Rail and Industrial Segments remains on disciplined growth organically and through acquisitions that improve the competitive positions of these businesses in core and adjacent markets. In the Company’s Metals & Minerals Segment, the focus is on improving the performance of the business through executing Project Orion, which is aimed at driving operational efficiencies from business structure simplification and operating practice standardization, establishing necessary protocols to facilitate better contract outcomes, addressing underperforming sites, and improving the mix of products and services. By executing these strategies, Harsco expects to realize improvements in return on invested capital (ROIC) and free cash flow in future years.
To learn more about Harsco’s strategy and commitment to enhancing shareholder value, click on the links in the left-hand navigation.
